ions for an invasion of Guatemala reported:\n\nArmy reserves of El Salvador are being called to active duty for an invasion of Guatemala from El Salvador by the Salvadoran, Nicaraguan and Honduran armies\n\nThe US Military Attache in San Salvador has visited Salvadoran army barracks but found no indications of preparations for such action, though rumors and speculation are rife", "token_count": 65, "token_end_0based": 64, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "western europe latin america 9 preparations for an invasion of guatemala reported army reserves of el salvador are being called to active duty for an invasion of guatemala from el salvador by the salvadoran nicaraguan and honduran armies the us military attache in san salvador has visited salvadoran army barracks but found no indications of preparations for such action though rumors and speculation are rife", "unred_source_page": 8}
